<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Hi,</p>

<p>The Zend_Log factory method should use</p>

<p>$log = new self();</p>

<p>instead of</p>

<p>$log = new Zend_Log();</p>

<p>to create the log instance, so it would be possible to extend Zend_Log without extending the factory method.</p>

